{
  "stem": "23622.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they had a very strong accent.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in other words, that were the Germans who got the station.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they addressed the people, and they sung our anthem.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "How dare.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then we heard more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we waited a little while.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we heard some noise and more noise.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we tried again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the anthem was sung again in Dutch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they had a fight.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they took over again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They just took over again.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there were just a few people who got our station, who had, of course, barged in or whatever, and took over.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they addressed our nation.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But that was quickly fixed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were gone again.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And our own people had, you know, the news again.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then we heard the news.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the whole day true.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, you can imagine the day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people who worked-- and then we found out that they had taken the bridges.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So people who worked on the other side of the city, where I came from, couldn't get through anymore.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I was just maybe one of the few who went over those bridges.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then more soldiers must have come in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were on the bridges.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And that, of course, is a long story.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You can, of course, tell a lot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But pretty soon, the marines, the Dutch Marines, were of course, got to know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it was very close to the bridges.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "They had a caserne over there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so the very first day, a big fight started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And it was a fight on the bridges.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "The Germans were on the bridges, and so were the marines.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "But the marines-- marines were very, very strong.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We had five-day war.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They fought five days on the bridges.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
